General.Name: LSI Industries Inc
General.Description: LSI Industries Inc. manufactures and distributes commercial lighting, graphics, and display solutions across strategic vertical markets. It also provides comprehensive project management services in support of large-scale product rollouts. Its products include non-residential indoor and outdoor lighting, print graphics, PC boards, digital signage, digital graphics, refrigerated and custom displays, and environmentally friendly in-store display fixtures. It provides services include professional services and security integration. Its portfolio spans several brands, including LSI Lighting, LSI Graphics, LSI Digital, Atlas Lighting, EMI Industries, and JSI Store Fixtures. It serves across vertical markets, such as automotive, infrastructure, parking, quick service restaurant, refueling and convenience store, sports venue, and warehouse. The company was founded in 1976 and is based in Cincinnati, Ohio.
